{"tid":1223561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《華爾基利暗殺行動》真係一套好好睇既戲","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T08:15:37.000Z","uid":8557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe2c6f6049d94de23497f1c0e6d883f4a46d815","tid":1223561,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"《華爾基利暗殺行動》（Valkyrie）<br />\n係一部2008年嘅歷史驚悚電影，由Bryan Singer執導。主演係湯告魯斯、簡尼夫班納、標尼菲。背景設定喺第二次世界大戰期間嘅納粹德國，<span style=\"color: red;\">講述1944年7月20日德國軍官暗殺元首阿道夫希特拉</span>同埋啟動女武神行動計劃嚟控制國家。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道最後當然係唔成功啦<br />\n但係呢一個極權獨裁既納粹黨下,仲要身為軍人都敢反希魔<br />\n舊時既人真係有風骨<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh-yue/b/bb/Valkyrie_2008_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh-yue%2Fb%2Fbb%2FValkyrie_2008_movie.jpg&h=5a372b41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"246d00605a7226d795ec5ed531320824e92340d3","tid":1223561,"uid":175722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7fe2c6f6049d94de23497f1c0e6d883f4a46d815","tid":1223561,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"《華爾基利暗殺行動》（Valkyrie）<br />\n係一部2008年嘅歷史驚悚電影，由Bryan Singer執導。主演係湯告魯斯、簡尼夫班納、標尼菲。背景設定喺第二次世界大戰期間嘅納粹德國，<span style=\"color: red;\">講述1944年7月20日德國軍官暗殺元首阿道夫希特拉</span>同埋啟動女武神行動計劃嚟控制國家。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道最後當然係唔成功啦<br />\n但係呢一個極權獨裁既納粹黨下,仲要身為軍人都敢反希魔<br />\n舊時既人真係有風骨<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh-yue/b/bb/Valkyrie_2008_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh-yue%2Fb%2Fbb%2FValkyrie_2008_movie.jpg&h=5a372b41&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:36:39.000Z","msg":"呢班軍人先係愛國，唔係盲目服從命令"},{"pid":"e6f640828e66f7aab868ea247aca1ce28c2a74c9","tid":1223561,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246d00605a7226d795ec5ed531320824e92340d3","tid":1223561,"uid":175722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"